                    <section style="box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;"><section style="color: rgb(52, 52, 52);line-height: 2;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">每一个打工人都以为自己在弹幕中才能找到有着相同打工魂的灵魂伴侣，而自己只能在生活中踽踽独行，不带走一片尘埃。阿桑在十七年前就预见到这种状况，她用沧桑充满故事的嗓音唱道<span style="box-sizing: border-box;">：“孤单，是一个人的狂欢，狂欢，是一群人的孤单。”</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 10px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="0.5623069" data-src="https://1-im.guokr.com/lz1FB5trxhmgdeR_7gnzel-JNaVxgBaMJyeD7nJ1mKbLAwAAIgIAAEpQ.jpg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="971" style="vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;" src="https://1-im.guokr.com/lz1FB5trxhmgdeR_7gnzel-JNaVxgBaMJyeD7nJ1mKbLAwAAIgIAAEpQ.jpg?imageView2/1/w/555/h/312"></section></section><section style="line-height: 1.4;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="text-align: center;white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 12px;color: rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing: border-box;">b站up主 泪腺战士丨b站</span></p></section><section style="color: rgb(52, 52, 52);line-height: 2;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">然而，这句话可能并不正确。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(72, 106, 183);box-sizing: border-box;">和一群人一起孤单的时候，陪伴你的一定是真人吗？</span></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">八九十年代出生的孩子习惯于沉溺在各种热血动画片里无法自拔，那时候的虚拟形象还只是停留在漫画书和显像管里，带着星辰大海的征途。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">不过沸血冲撞的年岁总是短暂，梦里温柔乡才是长久的话题。从风靡一时的纸片人再到永远16岁的二次元少女“初音未来”，虚拟偶像一步步俘获了少男少女们的心，也更一步步逼近了真人感。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">日本CG艺术家夫妻Teruyuki和Yuka Ishikawa在2015年一次偶然的机会，把自己的虚拟作品<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(72, 106, 183);box-sizing: border-box;">Saya</span></strong>的渲染照片发布到互联网上，吃瓜群众们纷纷表示吹弹可破，柔软乖巧，仿佛找到了自己的初恋。大家都以为她是日本某高中的网红校花，当得知这么漂亮的妹子其实是一个虚拟人物时，宅男们一边张大嘴巴惊讶，一边感到痛心。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 10px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="0.5625" data-src="https://1-im.guokr.com/DE7CD1q01p4lIuK5qNi64WxUahnKPuC7qdlxu3RuLWAABAAAQAIAAEpQ.jpg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1024" style="vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;" src="https://1-im.guokr.com/DE7CD1q01p4lIuK5qNi64WxUahnKPuC7qdlxu3RuLWAABAAAQAIAAEpQ.jpg?imageView2/1/w/555/h/312"></section></section><section style="line-height: 1.4;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="text-align: center;white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 12px;color: rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing: border-box;">Saya丨BBC</span></p></section><section style="color: rgb(52, 52, 52);line-height: 2;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">为了不辜负网友们的喜爱和感情寄托