e: 12px;color: rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing: border-box;">《爱，死亡和机器人-当酸奶统治世界》</span></p></section><section style="color: rgb(52, 52, 52);line-height: 2;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">在未来世界里，对赛博人抛出橄榄枝的电子娘可不止停留在2D卡通和3D渲染的形态，她们无孔不入，亦幻亦真。有的本是浑身腐臭的恶人，却通过脑机连接遥控着一副性感的躯壳在诱惑你，趁你欲火中烧之时给出致命一击，只为龌龊的金钱勾当。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">有人把爱人的基因写进萌萌哒的猫咪体内，试图让她在“噬元兽”体内获得永生，一直陪伴自己。如果说能拥有一个实体的电子娘是幸运的，天知道有多少人其实两手空空，只有一个脑内植入芯片所带来的种种幻觉。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br></p></section><section style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-right: 6px;padding-bottom: 6px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="padding-top: 6px;display: inline-block;background-color: rgb(220, 234, 244);box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-right: -6px;margin-bottom: -6px;margin-left: 6px;background-color: rgb(74, 116, 212);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);padding-right: 6px;padding-left: 6px;font-size: 20px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">作为”当代赛博人”的我们</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">该有哪些思考<br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(52, 52, 52);line-height: 2;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">当人工智能解决了所有生产力的困扰，当基因设计让情与欲走向两个极端，一类失去欲望，一类只剩欲望。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">于是你怕了，决定还是回到现实，却惊异地发现，我们对机器的依恋已经到了无法割舍的程度，并不是拥有了机械手臂或者机械大脑才能成为赛博人，<span style="color: rgb(72, 106, 183);box-sizing: border-box;">拥有了“电子器官”的我们，早已是“当代赛博人”了。</span>手机的电量告急让我们抓耳挠腮，我们与机器的捆绑越来越紧密。这种捆绑不仅仅会在生活中，更会体现在感情上。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(72, 106, 183);box-sizing: border-box;">在每一个个体逐渐变成赛博人的过程中，机器人真的可以陪伴我们不再孤单，甚至解决打工人的恋爱难题吗？亦或是我们终将失去感情中枢，孤身消逝？</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">在这个思考的起点，我们迎来了今年的<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(72, 106, 183);box-sizing: border-box;">首届腾讯科学脱口秀X-Talk</span></strong>。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 10px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="0.5625" data-src="https://3-im.guokr.com/i9Wqii2kaPl6wQ3n7eLwZzyBPam5BXovRe6baJGi4GjAAwAAHAIAAEpQ.jpg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="960" style="vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;" src="https://3-im.guokr.com/i9Wqii2kaPl6wQ3n7eLwZzyBPam5BXovRe6baJGi4GjAAwAAHAIAAEpQ.jpg?imageView2/1/w/555/h/312"></section></section><section style="color: rgb(52, 52, 52);line-height: 2;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">本届X-Talk以<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(72, 106, 183);box-sizing: border-box;">好奇心</span></strong>为出发点，用科学脱口秀的形式，面向更广阔的受众，邀请自然科学家、哲学社会学者、科幻作家、文化学者等科技和文化相关领域人士，探讨前沿科技的突破以及对人类社会，以及我们每个人生活和情感的影响。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section><section style="padding-left: 19px;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="width: 0px;margin-top: 2em;margin-right: 22px;margin-left: -19px;display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 0px;border-right: 20px solid rgb(220, 234, 244);border-top: 10px solid transparent !important;border-bottom: 10px solid transparent !important;box-sizing: border-box;"><section><svg viewbox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section><section style="width: 0px;margin-top: -19px;margin-bottom: -19px;margin-left: 3px;border-right: 18px solid rgb(220, 234, 244);box-sizing: border-box;border-top: 9px solid transparent !important;border-bottom: 9px solid transparent !important;"><section><svg viewbox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section><section style="padding: 10px;width: 100%;margin-top: -2em;min-height: 4em;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(220, 234, 244);box-shadow: rgba(255, 185, 149, 0) -2px 2px 5px;background-color: rgb(220, 234, 244);box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(220, 234, 244);line-height: 2;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(52, 52, 52);box-sizing: border-box;">快速发展的科技，会不会让我们生活变得更“魔幻”？</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section><section style="padding-right: 20px;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;padding: 10px;vertical-align: top;width: 100%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(255, 185, 149, 0);box-shadow: rgba(255, 185, 149, 0) 3px 3px 5px;background-color: rgb(232, 235, 246);margin-right: -20px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(88, 89, 89);line-height: 2;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(72, 106, 183);box-sizing: border-box;">腾讯集团副总裁、阅文集团首席执行官、腾讯影业首席执行官程武</span></strong>认为：</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">技术本身没有倾向性，取决于我们的价值观，取决于技术背后的人。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">同时，科技还可以成为传播真善美的载体，科技在促进文化繁荣的同时，文化也让科技变得更有温度，两者互为作用，从而搭建向善空间。</p></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 0px;margin-top: 2em;margin-left: 19px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 0px;border-left: 20px solid rgba(255, 185, 149, 0);border-top: 10px solid transparent !important;border-bottom: 10px solid transparent !important;box-sizing: border-box;"><section><svg viewbox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section><section style="width: 0px;margin-top: -19px;margin-bottom: -19px;border-left: 18px solid rgb(232, 235, 246);box-sizing: border-box;border-top: 9px solid transparent !important;border-bottom: 9px solid transparent !important;"><section><svg viewbox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(52, 52, 52);line-height: 2;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><section style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 2em;">X-Talk邀请了10多位跨界嘉宾大咖，介绍<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(72, 106, 183);box-sizing: border-box;">“人工智能”</span></strong>和<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(72, 106, 183);box-sizing: border-box;">“基因编辑”</span></strong>两项即将影响人类社会的先进科技，分享他们在对于未来科技和社会形态的好奇、思考和展望。</section><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 10px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="1.7777778" data-src="https://3-im.guokr.com/nGsN0Nnkp6ldTKXvuqCj7BgNG_moblHzf44S5dQ8HpM4BAAAgAcAAEpQ.jpg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;" src="https://3-im.guokr.com/nGsN0Nnkp6ldTKXvuqCj7BgNG_moblHzf44S5dQ8HpM4BAAAgAcAAEpQ.jpg?imageView2/1/w/555/h/986"></section></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 10px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="1.7777778" data-src="https://2-im.guokr.com/RUqFyQF-AHhuwLVWH1QVkBYoUs8jZLCpIUlbjWS3uVI4BAAAgAcAAEpQ.jpg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;" src="https://2-im.guokr.com/RUqFyQF-AHhuwLVWH1QVkBYoUs8jZLCpIUlbjWS3uVI4BAAAgAcAAEpQ.jpg?imageView2/1/w/555/h/986"></section></section><section style="color: rgb(52, 52, 52);line-height: 2;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(72, 106, 183);box-sizing: border-box;">说不定，听过腾讯X-Talk后，在不断思辨中，赛博人真就爱上电子娘了呢。</span></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(72, 106, 183);box-sizing: border-box;"><br></span></strong></p></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 10px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="2.008" data-src="https://1-im.guokr.com/vlgT6ma01NWJfUamFYaItKjGPKb1VGtVYVy5CRGxFaPuAgAA4gUAAEpQ.jpg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="750" style="vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;" src="https://1-im.guokr.com/vlgT6ma01NWJfUamFYaItKjGPKb1VGtVYVy5CRGxFaPuAgAA4gUAAEpQ.jpg?imageView2/1/w/555/h/1114"></section></section></section>
